reviews.text:
This place may be small compared with other houses, but the security guards are friendly and nice to people, the neighbourhood is usually quiet and there is a lot of food nearby. 
There is also a complex of shopping centres nearby and its is a 10 minute walk to Mong Kok and Yau Ma Tei ( a huge shopping complex and food complex) is a great place if you don’t have claustrophobia.
